metadata.name: Melodies from the Deep
metadata.description:
As the lightning struck and the waves roared, the giant octopus emerged from the depths of the purple sea, its long tentacles expertly maneuvering across the ivory keys of the grand piano, summoning melodies that echoed through the floating island, enchanting the skies with a hypnotic symphony that transcended the boundaries of time and space.

- Xyvora (2023)
